                    </div>
                    <div class="jump-line">
                        <strong><a href="#group-planning" class="jump-link">📅 Planning System</a></strong>
                        <span style="background:#28a745;color:#fff;padding:0 5px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.8em;">DB LIVE</span>:
                        <a href="#anchor-planning-system-project" class="jump-link">ProjectDetails</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-all-projects-list" class="jump-link">AllProjects</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-phase1" class="jump-link">DBEnvMgmt⏳</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-phase2" class="jump-link">SchemaModels🔜</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-5" class="jump-link">PlanController🔜</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-dailyplan-improvements" class="jump-link">DailyPlanUI🔜</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-6" class="jump-link">IntegrateTodo🔜</a> |
                        <a href="/Documentation/DailyPlan" class="jump-link">DynamicView↗</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="jump-line">
                        <strong><a href="#group-sync" class="jump-link">🔄 Synchronization & Standards</a></strong>:
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-16" class="jump-link">ProjectIDs</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-efficiency" class="jump-link">ProcessEfficiency</a> |
