                    </div>
                    <div class="jump-line">
                        <strong><a href="#group-file-mgmt" class="jump-link">📁 File Management System</a></strong>:
                        <a href="#group-file-mgmt" class="jump-link">Overview</a> |
                        Phase: <a href="#group-file-mgmt" class="jump-link">0✓</a>
                        1 2 3 4 5 6 (Pending)
                    </div>
                    <div class="jump-line">
                        <strong><a href="#group-workshops" class="jump-link">🎓 WorkShops System</a></strong>:
