    <div class="doc-metadata">
        <p><strong>File:</strong> [% file_path %] | <strong>Updated:</strong> [% formatted_date %]</p>

    </div>

    <details id="overview" class="overview-section">
        <summary>📋 Overview</summary>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>This document lists priority todos that are blocking development. <a href="#planning">View Priority List</a>.</p>
            
            <h4>🔧 Active Zenflow Workflows</h4>
            [% SET base_url = c.req.base.replace(':\d+/', ':') %]
            <ul>
                <li><strong>DailyPlanSystem:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]4000/Documentation/DailyPlan" target="_blank">new-task-3cda</a> <em>(port 4000)</em> - DailyPlan System Update</li>
                <li><strong>AIChatSystem:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]4001/Documentation/DailyPlan" target="_blank">aichatsystem-ef4e</a> <em>(port 4001)</em> - AI Chat System with Agent Architecture</li>
                <li><strong>SchemaManagement:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]4002/Documentation/DailyPlan" target="_blank">schema-management-system-7eb3</a> <em>(port 4002)</em> - Database Schema Management</li>
                <li><strong>InfrastructureHA:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]4003/Documentation/DailyPlan" target="_blank">new-task-9cf1</a> <em>(port 4003)</em> - High Availability & Disaster Recovery</li>
                <li><strong>WorkShops:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]4004/workshop" target="_blank">workshops-7d21</a> <em>(port 4004)</em> - Workshop Advertising System with Multi-Site Support</li>
                <li><strong>Users:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]4005/user/dashboard" target="_blank">users-e5b8</a> <em>(port 4005)</em> - User & Admin Management System with Email Verification and Role Management</li>
                <li><strong>ProjectConfig:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]3000/Documentation/DailyPlan" target="_blank">set-up-project-config-d327</a> <em>(ports 3000, 5000)</em> - Zenflow Project Configuration & Docker Container Testing</li>
                <li><strong>FileManagement:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]4006/admin/planning" target="_blank">new-task-bb05</a> <em>(port 4006)</em> - NFS-backed File Management System with multi-tier access control, duplicate detection, and workshop file sharing across SiteNames</li>
                <li><strong>UnifiedMailSystem:</strong> <a href="[% base_url %]4007/Documentation/DailyPlan" target="_blank">unified-mail-system-site-managed-2c53</a> <em>(port 4007)</em> - Unified Mail System — Site-Managed SMTP with PMG + Harper Integration</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; border-radius: 4px; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px;">
                <strong>⚠️ CRITICAL NAMING REQUIREMENT:</strong> Branch names MUST match worktree directory names. When Zenflow creates a workflow with a task name like "Update daily plan", it generates a directory name (e.g., <code>new-task-3cda</code>) but may create a different branch name (e.g., <code>UpdateDailyPlan-3cda</code>). This mismatch causes merge failures. <strong>Always rename the branch to match the directory name</strong> using <code>git branch -m OldName new-task-XXXX</code> to ensure consistency and successful merges.
            </div>
        </div>
    </details>

    <div id="planning" class="doc-section">
        <h2>Planning lists</h2>

        <!-- All Projects List from Database -->
        <div id="anchor-all-projects-list" class="nav-anchor"></div>
        <details class="sub-container" style="margin: 15px 0; border: 1px solid #2196F3; padding: 10px; background: #e3f2fd;">
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                📦 All Projects from Database (Reference - Future State Preview)
            </summary>
            <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <p><em>This shows all projects with their hierarchy. Eventually, all planning will be driven from the project database structure shown here.</em></p>
                [% SET all_db_projects = c.model('DBEncy').resultset('Project').search({}, { order_by => 'id' }) %]
                [% IF all_db_projects.count > 0 %]
                    [% FOREACH proj IN all_db_projects.all %]
                        [% UNLESS proj.parent_id %]
                        <details style="margin: 10px 0; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; background: white;">
                            <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;">
                                📁 [% proj.name %] (ID: [% proj.id %])
                            </summary>
                            <div style="margin: 10px 0 0 20px;">
                                <p><strong>Status:</strong> [% proj.status || 'Unknown' %] | <strong>Code:</strong> [% proj.project_code || 'N/A' %]</p>
                                <p><a href="/project/details?project_id=[% proj.id %]" target="_blank">View Full Details</a></p>

                                [% SET proj_subs = [] %]
                                [% FOREACH check_sub IN all_db_projects.all %]
                                    [% IF check_sub.parent_id == proj.id %]
                                        [% proj_subs.push(check_sub) %]
                                    [% END %]
                                [% END %]

                                [% IF proj_subs.size > 0 %]
                                    <details style="margin-top: 8px;">
                                        <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; color: #555;">
                                            📂 Sub-projects ([% proj_subs.size %])
                                        </summary>
                                        <div style="margin-left: 15px; font-size: 0.95em;">
                                            [% FOREACH sub IN proj_subs %]
                                                <div style="margin: 5px 0; padding: 5px; border-left: 2px solid #4CAF50; background: #f9f9f9;">
                                                    📄 [% sub.name %] (ID: [% sub.id %]) - [% sub.status || 'Unknown' %]
                                                </div>
                                            [% END %]
                                        </div>
                                    </details>
                                [% END %]
                            </div>
                        </details>
                        [% END %]
                    [% END %]
                [% ELSE %]
                    <p><em>No projects found.</em></p>
                [% END %]
            </div>
        </details>
        <!-- Group -1: Docker and K8s Management (ACTIVE) -->
        <div id="group-docker-k8s" class="nav-anchor"></div>
        <details id="group-docker-k8s-main" class="priority-group-container" open>
            <summary class="group-header">🐳 Docker and K8s Management</summary>
            <div class="priority-content">
                <h3>🐳 Docker and K8s Management</h3>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-in-progress">IN PROGRESS</span> | <strong>Priority:</strong> <span class="status-pending">HIGH</span></p>
                <p><strong>Zenflow Task:</strong> <code>set-up-project-config-d327</code> (ports 3000, 5000) | <strong>Branch:</strong> <code>set-up-project-config-d327</code></p>
                
                <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Reorganize and enhance Docker and Kubernetes related planning and documentation. Automate deployment process and setup High Availability in the server room.</p>

                <h4>📊 Docker and K8s Project from Database</h4>
                [% TRY %]
                    [% SET schema = c.model('DBEncy').schema %]
                    [% SET k8s_project = schema.resultset('Project').find(137) %]
                    
                    [% IF k8s_project %]
                        <div style="margin: 10px 0; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; background: white;">
                                <h3>[% k8s_project.name %] (Project ID: 137)</h3>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Description:</strong> [% k8s_project.description || 'Our Kurbuntes setup' %]</li>
                                    <li><strong>Start Date:</strong> [% k8s_project.start_date || '2026-02-06' %]</li>
                                    <li><strong>Status:</strong> [% k8s_project.status || 'In-Process' %]</li>
                                    <li><strong>Project Code:</strong> [% k8s_project.project_code || 'k8s' %]</li>
                                    <li><strong>Developer:</strong> [% k8s_project.developer_name || 'Shanta' %]</li>
                                </ul>

                                <p>
