            <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Migrate planning system from text-based files to database-driven dynamic system with role-based access control, audit trails, and integration with project management.</p>

            <h4>📋 Overview</h4>
            <p>Transform the Planning system from static text files into a fully dynamic database-driven application:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Role-based access control (Admin, Developer, User roles per site)</li>
                <li>Real-time todo management with drag-and-drop scheduling</li>
                <li>Multi-environment database support (Production, Staging, Dev)</li>
                <li>Comprehensive audit trails for all planning changes</li>
                <li>Project-documentation integration and mapping</li>
                <li>Dynamic daily, weekly, and monthly views</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>📊 Planning System Project from Database</h4>
            [% TRY %]
                [% SET schema = c.model('DBEncy').schema %]
                [% SET planning_project_search = schema.resultset('Project').search({ project_code => 'Planning' }).first %]
                [% SET planning_project = schema.resultset('Project').find(planning_project_search.id) IF planning_project_search %]

                [% IF planning_project %]
                    <div style="margin: 10px 0; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; background: white;">
                            <h3>[% planning_project.name %]</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Description:</strong> [% planning_project.description || 'No description' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Start Date:</strong> [% planning_project.start_date %]</li>
                                <li><strong>End Date:</strong> [% planning_project.end_date %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Status:</strong> [% planning_project.status %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Project Code:</strong> [% planning_project.project_code %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Project Size:</strong> [% planning_project.project_size %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Estimated Man Hours:</strong> [% planning_project.estimated_man_hours %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Developer Name:</strong> [% planning_project.developer_name %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Client Name:</strong> [% planning_project.client_name %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Comments:</strong> [% planning_project.comments || 'No comments' %]</li>
                            </ul>

                            <p>
                                <a href="/project/details?project_id=[% planning_project.id %]" target="_blank" style="color: #007bff;">View Details</a> |
                                <a href="/project/editproject?project_id=[% planning_project.id %]" target="_blank" style="color: #007bff;">Edit Project</a>
                            </p>

                            [% SET planning_todos = planning_project.todos.search({}, { order_by => 'sort_order' }) %]
                            [% IF planning_todos.count > 0 %]
                                <h4>📋 Todos for [% planning_project.name %] ([% planning_todos.count %])</h4>
                                <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;">
                                    [% FOREACH todo IN planning_todos.all %]
                                        <li style="margin: 5px 0; padding: 5px; border-left: 2px solid #FF9800; background: #fafafa;">
                                            [% IF todo.status == 'In-Process' %]⏳[% ELSIF todo.status == 'Completed' %]✅[% ELSE %]📌[% END %]
                                            [% todo.subject %]
                                            <br><small style="color: #666;">Status: [% todo.status %] | Due: [% todo.due_date %]</small>
                                            <br><a href="/todo/showtodo?record_id=[% todo.record_id %]" target="_blank" style="font-size: 0.9em;">View</a> |
                                            <a href="/todo/edittodo?record_id=[% todo.record_id %]" target="_blank" style="font-size: 0.9em;">Edit</a>
                                        </li>
                                    [% END %]
                                </ul>
                            [% ELSE %]
                                <p>No todos found for this project. <a href="/todo/addtodo?project_id=[% planning_project.id %]">Add a todo</a></p>
                            [% END %]

                            [% SET planning_subs = [] %]
                            [% SET all_projs_for_planning = c.model('DBEncy').resultset('Project').search({}, { order_by => 'id' }) %]
                            [% FOREACH check_sub IN all_projs_for_planning.all %]
                                [% IF check_sub.parent_id == planning_project.id %]
                                    [% planning_subs.push(check_sub) %]
                                [% END %]
                            [% END %]

                            [% IF planning_subs.size > 0 %]
                                <details style="margin-top: 10px;" open>
                                    <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; color: #555;">
                                        📂 Sub-Projects ([% planning_subs.size %])
                                    </summary>
                                    <div style="margin-left: 20px;">
                                        [% FOREACH subproject IN planning_subs %]
                                            <details class="subproject-item" style="margin: 8px 0; padding: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #4CAF50; background: #f5f5f5;">
                                                <summary style="cursor: pointer;">
                                                    [% IF subproject.status == 'In-Process' %]⏳[% ELSIF subproject.status == 'Completed' %]✅[% ELSE %]📄[% END %]
                                                    Sub-Project: [% subproject.name %] (ID: [% subproject.id %]) - <span style="color: #666;">[% subproject.status %]</span>
                                                </summary>
                                                <div style="margin: 8px 0 0 15px; font-size: 0.9em;">
                                                    <ul>
                                                        <li><strong>Description:</strong> [% subproject.description || 'No description' %]</li>
                                                        <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> [% subproject.start_date %] → [% subproject.end_date %]</li>
                                                        <li><strong>Status:</strong> [% subproject.status %]</li>
                                                        <li><strong>Project Code:</strong> [% subproject.project_code %]</li>
                                                        <li><strong>Estimated Hours:</strong> [% subproject.estimated_man_hours || 0 %]</li>
                                                        <li><strong>Developer:</strong> [% subproject.developer_name || 'Not assigned' %]</li>
                                                        <li><strong>Client:</strong> [% subproject.client_name || 'N/A' %]</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                    <p>
                                                        <a href="/project/details?project_id=[% subproject.id %]" target="_blank">View Details</a> |
                                                        <a href="/project/editproject?project_id=[% subproject.id %]" target="_blank">Edit</a>
                                                    </p>

                                                    [% SET sub_todos = subproject.todos.search({}, { order_by => 'sort_order' }) %]
                                                    [% IF sub_todos.count > 0 %]
                                                        <details style="margin-top: 8px;">
                                                            <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.9em;">
                                                                📋 Todos ([% sub_todos.count %])
                                                            </summary>
                                                            <div style="margin-left: 15px; font-size: 0.85em;">
                                                                <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;">
                                                                    [% FOREACH task IN sub_todos.all %]
                                                                        <li style="margin: 5px 0; padding: 5px; border-left: 2px solid #FF9800; background: #fafafa;">
                                                                            [% IF task.status == 'In-Process' %]⏳[% ELSIF task.status == 'Completed' %]✅[% ELSE %]📌[% END %]
                                                                            [% task.subject %]
                                                                            <br><small style="color: #666;">Status: [% task.status %] | Due: [% task.due_date %]</small>
                                                                            <br><a href="/todo/showtodo?record_id=[% task.record_id %]" target="_blank" style="font-size: 0.9em;">View</a> |
                                                                            <a href="/todo/edittodo?record_id=[% task.record_id %]" target="_blank" style="font-size: 0.9em;">Edit</a>
                                                                        </li>
                                                                    [% END %]
                                                                </ul>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </details>
                                                    [% ELSE %]
                                                        <p><em>No todos for this sub-project. <a href="/todo/addtodo?project_id=[% subproject.id %]">Add a todo</a></em></p>
                                                    [% END %]
                                                </div>
                                            </details>
                                        [% END %]
                                    </div>
                                </details>
                            [% ELSE %]
                                <p>No sub-projects found. <a href="/project/addproject?parent_id=[% planning_project.id %]">Add a sub-project</a></p>
                            [% END %]
                    </div>
                [% ELSE %]
                    <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
                        <p><strong>⚠️ Project Not Found:</strong> Planning System project with code "Planning" not found in database.</p>
                        <p><strong>Action Required:</strong> Create the Planning project via <a href="/project/addproject" target="_blank" style="color: #007bff;">Add Project form</a> with project_code "Planning".</p>
                        <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Create main project: "Planning System Migration"</li>
                            <li>Create 15 sub-projects for Phases 0-14 (P0 already complete)</li>
                            <li>Link todos to each phase sub-project</li>
                        </ol>
                        <p><strong>For reference:</strong> See <a href="/project/details?project_id=157" target="_blank" style="color: #007bff;">API System Project (ID 157)</a> for example structure.</p>
                    </div>
                [% END %]
            [% CATCH %]
                <p style="color: #d9534f;"><strong>Error:</strong> Unable to fetch Planning System project from database. [% error.info %]</p>
            [% END %]

            <h4>🚀 Implementation Workflow: Phases P0-P14 (Text Reference — being migrated to DB)</h4>
            <p style="background:#d4edda;border:1px solid #28a745;border-radius:4px;padding:8px 12px;font-size:0.9em;">
                <strong>📊 DB-tracked:</strong> These phases are now tracked as DB todos 502–516 under
                <a href="/project/details?project_id=138" style="color:#155724;">Planning System project (id=138)</a> →
                sub-projects 186–190. View them via the <a href="/Documentation/DailyPlan#planning" style="color:#155724;">PLANNING tab</a>.
                As each phase is completed and verified in DB, its text section below will be removed.
            </p>

            <div id="anchor-phase0-complete" class="nav-anchor"></div>
            <!-- Phase 0: Planning System Analysis & Integration Mapping -->
            <details class="phase-container" style="margin: 15px 0; border: 2px solid #4CAF50; padding: 10px; background: #e8f5e9;">
                        <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em;">
                            ✅ Phase 0: Planning System Analysis & Integration Mapping (COMPLETE)
                        </summary>
                        <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-completed">COMPLETE</span></p>
                            <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Analyze existing text-based planning system and map it to future database-driven Project/Planning structure.</p>

                            <h5>📋 Tasks:</h5>
                            <ul>
                                <li>✅ 0.1: Inventory Existing Planning Content</li>
                                <li>✅ 0.2: Analyze Existing Projects</li>
                                <li>✅ 0.3: Design Project-Planning Integration Schema</li>
                                <li>✅ 0.4: Plan Migration Strategy</li>
