                        <li><a href="/Documentation/TodoSystemDocumentation" target="_blank">2025-01-20 Todo System Documentation</a></li>
                    </ul>

                    <p><em>For full implementation details, see original plan content below in archived Group 6.</em></p>
                </div>
            </details>
