            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-in-progress">IN PROGRESS - Phase 0 COMPLETE</span> | <strong>Priority:</strong> <span class="status-pending">HIGH</span></p>
            <p><strong>Zenflow Task:</strong> <code>workshops-7d21</code> (port 4004) | <strong>Branch:</strong> <code>workshops-7d21</code></p>

            <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Comprehensive platform for managing and advertising educational workshops across multiple sites with role-based access control, participant management, PowerPoint integration, mailing lists, and content development tools.</p>

            <h4>📋 Overview</h4>
            <p>Transform basic workshop CRUD operations into a full-featured workshop advertising and management system:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Multi-site workshop advertising with public/private visibility</li>
                <li>Workshop leader role management and permissions</li>
                <li>Online registration workflow with capacity limits and waitlists</li>
                <li>PowerPoint presentation upload/download for participants</li>
                <li>Online content development with rich text editor</li>
                <li>Workshop mailing lists with email history tracking</li>
                <li>File upload/download system for workshop materials</li>
                <li>Comprehensive authorization (CSC admin god-level, site-scoped admins/leaders)</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>📊 WorkShops Project from Database</h4>
            [% TRY %]
                [% SET schema = c.model('DBEncy').schema %]
                [% SET workshop_project = schema.resultset('Project').find(73) %]
                
                [% IF workshop_project %]
                    <div style="margin: 10px 0; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; background: white;">
                            <h3>[% workshop_project.name %] (Project ID: 73)</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Description:</strong> [% workshop_project.description || 'Workshop module for managing and advertising educational workshops across multiple sites' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Start Date:</strong> [% workshop_project.start_date || '2024-01-01' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>End Date:</strong> [% workshop_project.end_date || 'TBD' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Status:</strong> [% workshop_project.status || 'In-Process' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Project Code:</strong> [% workshop_project.project_code || 'WORKSHOP' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Project Size:</strong> [% workshop_project.project_size || 'Large' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Estimated Man Hours:</strong> [% workshop_project.estimated_man_hours || '120' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Developer Name:</strong> [% workshop_project.developer_name || 'Development Team' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Client Name:</strong> [% workshop_project.client_name || 'Internal' %]</li>
                                <li><strong>Comments:</strong> [% workshop_project.comments || 'Multi-site workshop advertising system with participant management and PowerPoint integration' %]</li>
                            </ul>

                            <p>
                                <a href="/project/details?project_id=8" target="_blank" style="color: #007bff;">View Details</a> |
                                <a href="/project/editproject?project_id=8" target="_blank" style="color: #007bff;">Edit Project</a>
                            </p>

                            [% SET workshop_todos = workshop_project.todos.search({}, { order_by => 'sort_order' }) %]
                            [% IF workshop_todos.count > 0 %]
                                <h4>📋 Todos for [% workshop_project.name %] ([% workshop_todos.count %])</h4>
                                <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;">
                                    [% FOREACH todo IN workshop_todos.all %]
                                        <li style="margin: 5px 0; padding: 5px; border-left: 2px solid #FF9800; background: #fafafa;">
                                            [% IF todo.status == 'In-Process' %]⏳[% ELSIF todo.status == 'Completed' %]✅[% ELSE %]📌[% END %]
                                            [% todo.subject %]
                                            <br><small style="color: #666;">Status: [% todo.status %] | Due: [% todo.due_date %]</small>
                                            <br><a href="/todo/showtodo?record_id=[% todo.record_id %]" target="_blank" style="font-size: 0.9em;">View</a> |
                                            <a href="/todo/edittodo?record_id=[% todo.record_id %]" target="_blank" style="font-size: 0.9em;">Edit</a>
                                        </li>
                                    [% END %]
                                </ul>
                            [% ELSE %]
