        <!-- Group: File Management System -->
        <details id="group-file-mgmt" class="priority-group-container" open>
            <summary class="group-header">📁 File Management System</summary>
            <div class="priority-content">

            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-in-progress">IN PROGRESS - Phase 0 COMPLETE</span> | <strong>Priority:</strong> <span class="status-pending">HIGH</span></p>
            <p><strong>Zenflow Task:</strong> <code>new-task-bb05</code> | <strong>Branch:</strong> <code>new-task-bb05</code></p>

            <p><strong>Objective:</strong> Production-ready NFS-backed file management system with multi-tier access control, duplicate detection, file renaming, and workshop file sharing across SiteNames.</p>

            <h4>📋 Overview</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>CSC Admin manages NFS directory allocations per SiteName (<code>nfs_directory</code> table)</li>
                <li>SiteName Admins browse and manage files scoped to their allocated directories</li>
                <li>All files tracked in the <code>files</code> DB table (already exists)</li>
                <li>Duplicate detection by file name + size on upload and NFS sync</li>
                <li>Atomic file rename: filesystem + DB updated together, DB rolled back on FS failure</li>
                <li>Workshop file sharing across SiteNames via <code>WorkshopResource.access_level</code></li>
                <li>Server-room services (Proxmox etc.) tracked read-only via NFS sync</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>🗺️ Delivery Phases</h4>

            <details class="priority-container" open>
                <summary><strong>Phase 0 — Navigation &amp; Admin Dashboard</strong> <span class="status-completed">COMPLETE</span></summary>
